response.original_title: Pete Murray: A Year In The Sun
response.overview: This new DVD release from Pete Murray will follow his year leading up to, including and after the release of his latest album "See The Sun". Features never before seen footage as well as fantastic clips from many International live shows contribute to making this an amazing DVD. It's a must have for any fans or any new people discovering Pete Murray. It a complete overview of the last amazing year.
response.title: Pete Murray: A Year In The Sun
